{"tid":39643,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"巨乳人妻入～原來周姐撚一早寫咗首歌係講你！","createTime":"2016-12-14T16:43:02.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-14T16:50:38.000Z","uid":31748,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"277c1adf1a2caa844dccb2a2a43cb98f576e3c6a","tid":39643,"uid":31748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T16:43:02.000Z","msg":"[img]<a href=\"http://i.imgur.com/OdapOx1.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FOdapOx1.jpg&d=vUg23RdbbGWRY1NFBUUeLmN6obqfy%2FNc7jg2IsrTbnE%3D&h=496ae6d2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://i.imgur.com/OdapOx1.jpg</a><br />\n[/img]<br />\n<br />\n把她忘記<br />\n重複告訴自己<br />\n熟悉不再熟悉<br />\n但清晰卻還是一樣清晰<br />\n<br />\n喔～去吧<br />\n隨著右手旋律<br />\n忘了左手的委屈<br />\n就算沒伴奏也可以繼續<br />\n<br />\n前進 找尋新的記憶和空氣<br />\n放晴 等雨說放棄<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n在有眼淚的雨裡<br />\n哪裡都是你<br />\n擦乾是否就看不見你<br />\n腦海裡 你的笑容太徹底<br />\n徹底把我囚禁在你的呼吸<br />\n我跟著哭泣<br />\n<br />\n在有眼淚的雨裡<br />\n哪裡都是你<br />\n抱緊你是我逃離的距離<br />\n太擁擠 我在你的世界裡<br />\n看不清楚的是你還是自己<br />\n我們都在等雨停<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/3gtzsip8\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F3gtzsip8&h=d8bc8bc6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"879ad0e36f6ca5cf1bc6c1b3519cc0ca1c23fd23","tid":39643,"uid":90,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T16:43:45.000Z","msg":"同佢好熟<br />\n當年想溝我，拒絕咗"},{"pid":"012491507fb419bf504ab375f4a4969aab21ebb9","tid":39643,"uid":38293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T16:44:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>同佢好熟<br />\n當年想溝我，拒絕咗</blockquote><br />\n因為你愛我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a7ec4fff87a59dd178f725452d981a9d491d1a8","tid":39643,"uid":90,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0